{
  "page": "Grey emperors",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>grey emperors</b> were an ancient ruling dynasty of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Empire_of_Yi_Ti\" title=\"Golden Empire of Yi Ti\">Golden Empire of Yi Ti</a>. They ruled from the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Yin\" title=\"Yin\">Yin</a> and their family name was <b>Har</b>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_yellow_emperors\">Known yellow emperors</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grey_emperors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known yellow emperors\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/God-Emperor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"God-Emperor\">Emperor</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Har_Loi\" title=\"Har Loi\">Har Loi</a>, first of grey emperor</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_notes\">References and notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grey_emperors&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_yi_ti.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp